---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms and Conditions | BrewYourBeing">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-28 pb-20 bg-brew-cream min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif text-brew-brown mb-8">Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        <p><strong class="text-brew-brown">Effective Date:</strong> February 2026</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>Welcome to BrewYourBeing. By accessing or using our website and services, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree, please do not use our services.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">2. Services</h2>
        <p>BrewYourBeing provides clinical psychology and psychotherapy services including individual therapy, group therapy, couple therapy, and psychological assessments. Sessions are conducted by Niharika Singh Bhadauria, a licensed Clinical Psychologist recognized by the Rehabilitation Council of India.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">3. Appointments & Booking</h2>
        <p>All appointments are booked through our online booking form. Submission of the form constitutes a request for an appointment, not a confirmed booking. Confirmation will be provided via email or phone within 24-48 hours.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">4. Cancellation & Rescheduling</h2>
        <p>Clients are requested to provide at least 24 hours notice for cancellations or rescheduling. Failure to do so may result in a cancellation fee or loss of the session.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">5. Confidentiality</h2>
        <p>All information shared during sessions is kept strictly confidential in accordance with professional ethical guidelines. Exceptions apply only where required by law or in cases of imminent risk to safety.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">6. Professional Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>Our services are not a substitute for emergency medical care. If you are in crisis or experiencing a medical emergency, please contact emergency services immediately.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content on this website, including text, graphics, logos, and images, is the property of BrewYourBeing and is protected by applicable copyright laws.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">8. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>BrewYourBeing reserves the right to modify these Terms and Conditions at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">9. Contact</h2>
        <p>For any questions regarding these terms, please reach out at <a href="mailto:brewyourbeing@gmail.com" class="text-brew-light hover:text-brew-brown underline">brewyourbeing@gmail.com</a> or call <a href="tel:+916263121929" class="text-brew-light hover:text-brew-brown underline">+91 6263-121929</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/" class="text-brew-brown hover:text-brew-light transition-colors font-medium">&larr; Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
